added.axolotl_tempt_items: • Items in this tag can be used to tempt axolotls.
added.candles:
• Cakes use this tag to determine if a candle item can be placed on it or not.
  • Adding items to this tag has no effect.
added.cluster_max_harvestables: • When amethyst clusters are broken with an item in this tag, they drop 4 amethyst shards.
added.fox_food: • Foxes treat items in this tag like they do sweet berries.
added.freeze_immune_wearables: • Entities with an item in this tag in any armor slot do not freeze.
added.ignored_by_piglin_babies:
• Baby piglins do not attempt to pick up items in this tag. Baby piglins still follow the other rules adult piglins follow.
  • Takes precedence over piglin_food, and piglin_loved item tags when an item is in both.
added.occludes_vibration_signals: • As thrown entities, items in this tag do not trigger vibrations.
added.piglin_food:
• Piglins can "eat" items in this tag.
    • Eating refers to the piglin seeking out and picking up an item without appearing in its inventory, thus vanishing.
